verbose_text: The equivalent of the mouse ERSE stage was at E10.5 in pig and E14.0 in cattle, with OCT4 expression demarcating a near perfect radially symmetrical epiblast, and NANOG, SOX2 and NODAL expression demarcating the entire epiblast but showing an asymmetric distribution within it as previously described for the mouse [XREF_FIG A; Fig. S1A-C].
